2.2 PIE PLOT

ds_salaries1$experience_level <- as.factor(ds_salaries1$experience_level)

experience_counts <- table(ds_salaries1$experience_level)

percentages <- round(100 * experience_counts / sum(experience_counts), 1)
labels <- paste(names(experience_counts), "\n", experience_counts, " (", percentages, "%)", sep="")

pie(experience_counts, main = "Pie Chart of Experience Levels", labels = labels)
